      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Who also declared unto us your love in the Spirit - The love wrought in you by the Holy Spirit. It was not mere natural affection, but love worked in their hearts by the agency of the Holy Spirit. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
