  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "8. your love—(Col 1:4); \"to all the saints.\"",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "in the Spirit—the sphere or element IN which alone true love is found; as distinguished from the state of those \"in the flesh\" (Ro 8:9). Yet even they needed to be stirred up to greater love (Col 3:12-14). Love is the first and chief fruit of the Spirit (Ga 5:22).",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
